name: Jumping Moto - Tricky Mater
description:
Jumping Moto - Tricky Mater!!!
Exciting level and interesting missions are attractiveness of this game. You have to understand the aim and drive multiple bike with different riders. Take care of the mines and survive against sudden falls and mishaps. Most stunning game for all age users where all aspects like enjoyment, thrill and precautions will utilize while driving.
Feature:
Realistic interface and rider animation
Tricky tracks and pathways
A game of nonstop amusement and thrill
Good sound effects and interface
Multi camera angles mode
